spec_data.Name: python3-seesaw
spec_data.License: WTFPL and MIT and Public Domain
spec_data.Description:
An asynchronous toolkit for distributed web processing. Written in
Python and named after its behavior, it supports concurrent downloads,
uploads, etc.

This toolkit is well-known for Archive Team projects. It also powers
the ArchiveTeam warrior.
